(text "J302/J303 are one-to-one traces only." (at 389.89 383.54 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid ff11939c-db53-43d7-ab18-8131fbcdf406))
(text "Use for power/menu/volume/brightness keypad or resistor ladder." (at 389.89 391.16 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid b3c28b9f-6268-49f9-8637-5fa88fcd59fa))
(text "Final pin order must follow the opened monitor's button board." (at 389.89 398.78 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid c41ba344-babd-42f7-b866-22efbd6c63b7))
(text "NOTES:" (at 20.32 480.06 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid abb27383-3f5c-4931-9f66-b359189ab3ca))
(text "This retained-controller path avoids external cables while preserving the Intehill controller, touch board, and speakers." (at 20.32 487.68 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 6b507324-866e-422f-8308-c04964bda9e9))
(text "HDMI carries display audio to the monitor's integrated speakers; no separate speaker amplifier is added in this pass." (at 20.32 495.3 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 5c4e0169-47d5-4a68-aaf8-a3589d4801d2))
(text "DDIB_TX3 is HDMI TMDS clock; DDIB_TX2/1/0 map to HDMI data2/1/0 per the Mu HDMI reference direction." (at 20.32 502.92 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid b9e03f92-b7f8-4bd2-9bc5-d6c4b4956f0e))
(text "Keep this path HDMI 2.0/18Gbps capable end-to-end for 2560x1600@120; avoid HDMI 1.4-only cables/adapters/ESD." (at 20.32 510.54 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 1d2dda92-ae7c-422d-81ab-fe4da655fe0e))
(text "U303 lets the EC gate monitor power with soft-start/current limit; set ILIM/dVdT after measuring monitor inrush/current." (at 20.32 518.16 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 264a5802-b825-42f1-a1cb-927ec9f2ae46))
(text "J301 is a 5V-only Type-C source with 10k Rp for 3A advertisement; add PD only if the monitor demands it." (at 20.32 525.78 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid a4e21fb0-21f4-42b6-a6b9-b836bab5f5a5))
(text "Mechanical choice remains open: disassembled internal HDMI/USB-C plugs, low-profile adapters, or raw-panel replacement." (at 20.32 533.4 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid d169ede7-581b-4a05-8f8d-735b9aa96330))
